    <p class="text-gray-300"><span class="math">$\\alpha(x) = \\frac{p_S \\lambda \\cdot A}{p_S \\lambda - p_T \\lambda} (e^{(p_S \\lambda - p_T \\lambda)x} - 1) + \\alpha_0 p_T \\lambda + A \\Longrightarrow</span>$</p>

